### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5200/api
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### 1. Register (Crear usuario de prueba)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Usuario Test",
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "password": "Test123!",
  "phoneNumber": "912345678",
  "role": "User"
}

### 2. Login (Para obtener un token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

### 3. Get Current User (Token v√°lido - Obtiene usuario del JWT)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/user
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Logout (Revocar el token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Intentar usar el token revocado (Debe fallar con 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/user
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

